            li#link2: a(href='https://twitter.com/brandonrhoward1'): i.fa.fa-twitter

    #home.row.full-panel
      .left-side.col-sm-6
        img.profile-mobile.img-circle.center-block.visible-xs(src="img/brandon-profile-grey.jpg")
        h1 Software craftsman & Rubyist in training.
        i(class="fa fa-quote-left fa-3x pull-left fa-border")
        p.
            Thanks for dropping by! I've recently graduated from<a href="http://nashvillesoftwareschool.com/">
            Nashville Software School</a>, a six-month, thirty-five-hour-a-week coding bootcamp.
            The program consisted of three months of front-end development training and then three months of server-side training.
            While I was there, I learned all about the magic that is software development. I also
            learned a lot about myself. I am now seeking a thoughtful, passionate team to help me hone my new craft.

      .right-side.col-sm-6

    #skills.skills.row.full-panel.text-center
      .row
        .col-sm-10.col-sm-offset-1.col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
          h1 Tech prowess
          p.
            The vast majority of class time was spent hacking. I worked in small teams on group projects,
            and I also spent plenty of time doing solo projects as well.

      #myCarousel.carousel.center-block.hidden-xs.slide(data-ride="carousel")

        .carousel-inner.center-block(role="listbox")
          .item.active
            img.img-responsive.img-rounded.center-block(src="img/code-shots/bounty.png")
            div.text-center
              h4.highlight.
                <a href="https://github.com/brayhoward/swap">Bounty</a>,
                a social networking application built with Rails.

          .item
            img.img-responsive.img-rounded.center-block(src="img/code-shots/linked-list.png")
            div.text-center
