                <a href="https://github.com/brayhoward/linked_list_cohort_huckleberry">Linked list</a>
                data structure constructed with base Ruby.

          .item
            img.img-responsive.img-rounded.center-block(src="img/code-shots/calrb.png")
            div.text-center
              h4.highlight.
                Ruby implamentation of the Unix <a href="https://github.com/brayhoward/calendar_app">`Cal`</a> program
          .item
            img.img-responsive.img-rounded.center-block(src="img/code-shots/game-won-2.png")
            div.text-center
              h4.highlight.
                <a href="https://game-won.firebaseapp.com/?">Game-won</a>, tic-tac-toe built with javaScript.


